p://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coordinated_Universal_Time\" title=\"Coordinated Universal Time\">UTC</a>+4)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Right-_and_left-hand_traffic\" title=\"Right- and left-hand traffic\">Drives on the</a></th>\n<td>left</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Country_code_top-level_domain\" title=\"Country code top-level domain\">Internet TLD</a></th>\n<td><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/.sc\" title=\".sc\">.sc</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_country_calling_codes\" title=\"List of country calling codes\">Calling code</a></th>\n<td>248</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p><b>Seychelles</b> (pronounced <span title=\"Pronunciation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)\" class=\"IPA\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:IPA_for_English\" title=\"Wikipedia:IPA for English\">/se…™Àà É…õl/</a></span> or <small>IPA:&#160;</small><span title=\"Pronunciation in IPA\" class=\"IPA\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:IPA\" title=\"Wikipedia:IPA\">[/se…™Àà É…õlz/]</a></span> in English and <span title=\"Pronunciation in IPA\" class=\"IPA\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:IPA_for_French\" title=\"Wikipedia:IPA for French\">[se É…õl]</a></span> in French), officially the <b>Republic of Seychelles</b> (<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/French_language\" title=\"French language\">French</a>: <span lang=\"fr\" xml:lang=\"fr\"><i>R√©publique des Seychelles</i></span>; <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Seychellois_Creole\" title=\"Seychellois Creole\">Creole</a>: <i>Repiblik Sesel</i>), is an <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Archipelago\" title=\"Archipelago\">archipelago</a> <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Country\" title=\"Country\">nation</a> of 115 islands in the <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Indian_Ocean\" title=\"Indian Ocean\">Indian Ocean</a>, some 1,500&#160;kilometres (932&#160;mi) east of mainland <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Africa\" title=\"Africa\">Africa</a>, northeast of the island of <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Madagascar\" title=\"Madagascar\">Madagascar</a>. Other nearby island countries and territories include <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zanzibar\" title=\"Zanzibar\">Zanzibar</a> to the west, <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mauritius\" title=\"Mauritius\">Mauritius</a> and <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/R%C3%A9union\" title=\"R√©union\">R√©union</a> to the south, <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Comoros\" title=\"Comoros\">Comoros</a> and <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mayotte\" title=\"Mayotte\">Mayotte</a> to the southwest, and the <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maldives\" title=\"Maldives\">Maldives</a> to the northeast. The Seychelles has the smallest population of any African state <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_countries_by_population\" class=\"external autonumber\" rel=\"nofollow\">[1]</a>, <a href=\"http://goafrica.about.com/od/africatraveltips/a/africafacts.htm\" class=\"external autonumber\" rel=\"nofollow\">[2]</a></p>\n<table id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\">\n<tr>\n<td>\n<div id=\"toctitle\"'),(131,NULL,'Liberia',NULL,'upload/Liberia.txt',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2009-10-22 08:27:30','	<h1 id=\"firstHeading\" class=\"firstHeading\">Liberia</h1>\n		<div id=\"bodyContent\">\n			<h3 id=\"siteSub\"></h3>\n			<div id=\"contentSub\"></div>\n									<div id=\"jump-to-nav\">Jump to: <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Liberia#column-one\">navigation</a>, <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Liberia#searchInput\">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->\n			<div class=\"dablink\">This article is about the country in Africa.  For the city, see <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Liberia,_Costa_Rica\" title=\"Liberia, Costa Rica\">Liberia, Costa Rica</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox geography vcard\" style=